      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "My sources confirm the movement of materiel near Sector 4, but the intelligence suggests these are primarily defensive stockpiles being rotated for routine readiness drills, not offensive preparations. We have zero credible evidence of combat-ready units being deployed to the forward depots, which is the most significant differentiator. I'd advise presenting this as a strategic repositioning of assets ahead of the summit, which is a standard diplomatic maneuver, not a sign of impending conflict.",
